## Accessibility Requirements

### Color Contrast
- **Text on background**: Minimum 4.5:1 ratio (WCAG AA)
- **Large text**: Minimum 3:1 ratio
- **Interactive elements**: 3:1 ratio for focus indicators
- **Charts**: Patterns/textures in addition to color

### Focus Management
- **Focus indicators**: 3px outline, slate-500 color
- **Skip links**: Hidden until focused
- **Tab order**: Logical, predictable sequence
- **Keyboard navigation**: All interactive elements accessible

### Screen Reader Support
- **Semantic HTML**: Proper heading hierarchy, landmarks
- **ARIA labels**: Descriptive labels for complex UI
- **Chart descriptions**: Text alternatives for visual data
- **State announcements**: Dynamic content changes announced

### Motion & Animation
- **Reduced motion**: Respect user preferences
- **Subtle transitions**: 200ms duration maximum
- **Purpose-driven**: Animation serves usability, not decoration
- **Accessibility escape**: Option to disable animations

